+### Skipping lifecycle steps
+
+You can skip any of the lifecycle steps (`bump`, `changelog`, `commit`, `tag`),
+by adding the following to your package.json:
+
+```json
+{
+  "standard-version": {
+    "skip": {
+      "changelog": true
+    }
+  }
